{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4ec88d141d","title":"关于发表中共中央声明的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5ac871abd3","index":0,"year":1963,"month":6,"day":30,"articleId":"4ec88d141d"}],"tags":[{"id":"5bfa9ca15d","name":"宣言","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/45-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji45":{"comments":[{"id":"a0a1ed3973","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国共产党中央委员会1963年7月1日声明。声明说，中共中央决定，组成以总书记邓小平为团长的中共代表团，参加7月5日将在莫斯科举行的中苏两党会谈。声明还对中共代表团提出要求，并期望两党会谈能够取得积极的成果。这个声明在1963年7月1日《人民日报》上发表。"},{"id":"9e3fb856fa","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在康生（中共中央政治局候补委员、中央书记处书记）1963年6月30日给毛泽东的信上。信中说，赫鲁晓夫的报告全文已收到译出，其中攻击中国党的一段，另纸抄上。邓小平说，原中共中央声明稿可以定下，不要改了。在今晚8时政治局通过后，今晚即可广播，明天即见报。所说赫鲁晓夫报告，是指他在苏共中央6月18日至21日召开的全体会议上发表的长篇讲话。"}],"contents":[{"id":"c2a7151b40","type":"title","text":"关于发表中共中央声明的批语2","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d"},{"id":"a0a1ed3973","type":"paragraph","text":"康生同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d"},{"id":"9e3fb856fa","type":"paragraph","text":"已看过，同意小平同志意见","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d"},{"id":"930201dc85","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d"},{"id":"953e8fdea8","type":"paragraph","text":"州日下午七时","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d"}],"page":{"id":"d068559207","publicationId":"maoquanji45","articleId":"4ec88d141d","start":458,"end":458}}}},"__N_SSG":true}